Hi @dnpawate Is this a new project integrating TF?
As long as you configure repositories like below, it should work:
repositories {
maven {
url 'https://google.bintray.com/tensorflow'
}
}
If you still cannot make it work, would you mind sharing your (2) build.gradles? You can delete your other dependencies / app names etc.

